content:
Service Cloud Voice minutes and telephony minutes are different. Here's how they're charged:

A one-minute inbound call that uses IVR only: 1 minute
A one-minute outbound call from an agent: 1 minute
An inbound call handled by two agents for 2 minutes total: 2 minutes (charged per agent)
An inbound call handled by an agent, then transferred outside the organization lasting 5 minutes: 1 minute (for agent handling) + 5 minutes (for transferred call)

Note: Transferred calls are not charged as Service Cloud Voice minutes.
title: Understanding Service Cloud Minutes and Telephony Charges
